      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering a visceral induction note and linear power delivery. This example features the sought-after 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal mechanical grip. The chassis is anchored by a carbon-fiber reinforced plastic (CFRP) roof, significantly reducing the center of gravity. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of track use or rock chipping, while the interior leather remains supple with a factory matte finish. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
